{"tid":2183616,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區會反檢測中心 DO拒支援","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T04:49:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1eea6cb9725c9ce5dd19a335e5491940d47526b0","tid":2183616,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/UGCBIL5BFVDFVNGMAJXG4GUB54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FUGCBIL5BFVDFVNGMAJXG4GUB54%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7qRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=a370dd10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FUGCBIL5BFVDFVNGMAJXG4GUB54%2F&h=c972c712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/UGCBIL5BFVDFVNGMAJXG4GUB54/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n區會反檢測中心 DO拒支援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/woAEllabdg68obabm9WlwaEtQ6A=/6039x4026/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E6T6PJZIIVARVHCVDCLX2HIJEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwoAEllabdg68obabm9WlwaEtQ6A%3D%2F6039x4026%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE6T6PJZIIVARVHCVDCLX2HIJEY.jpg&h=e6e81e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中西區民政專員梁子琪（右）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中西區及油尖旺區議會昨分別開會，討論政府在區內設武漢肺炎檢測中心，但卻未有諮詢區會和居民，兩個區會均對此作出譴責及反對，而中西區民政專員（DO）梁子琪更以討論違《區議會條例》拒作支援，又稱事前有諮詢律政司意見，但拒公開內容。<br />\n<br />\n多名民主派油尖旺區議員質疑政府為何未作諮詢，即宣佈在區內設立五個檢測中心。民主派區議員李國權指麥花臣匯居民和業委會一直強烈反對在麥花臣球場設立檢測中心，但。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引律政司意見 指屬「全港性」<br />\n<br />\n中西區區會同樣召開特別會議討論檢測計劃，當中一份文件提及檢測中心貼近民居，區會強烈反對在完成地區諮詢前開始全民。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨許智峯斥責梁子琪濫用職權，指梁不但「零諮詢」，亦沒負起邀請部門出席會議的相關責任。"}]}